SummaryEnglish: Follows several young women who each do their utmost to seduce their senpai.

1.TitleEnglish: The Coworker is Suffering from Social Inequality
Due To A Mix-up At The Hotel, Two Coworkers End Up Sharing A Room On A Business Trip
1.SummaryEnglish: Douki-chan tries to take advantage of the mix-up on a business trip to seduce a coworker she likes.

2.TitleEnglish: My coworker and I were in the elevator together and then we were trapped inside together
2.SummaryEnglish: Douki-chan and the coworker she likes are trapped in the elevator together. Can she use this opportunity to get closer to him?

3.TitleEnglish: The Junior Who Gives Chocolate On Valentine's Day At Work
3.SummaryEnglish: Douki-chan makes chocolates for the coworker she likes, but her Junior steals him away.

4.TitleEnglish: My Coworker Who Came Back To Pick Up What He Left Behind
4.SummaryEnglish: Douki-kun comes back to the restaurant and sees that Douki-chan has fallen asleep. He helps her get home, and then...?

5.TitleEnglish: A Coworker Who Was Looking Forward To A White Day Gift...
5.SummaryEnglish: March 14th is White Day, when men who received chocolates on Valentine's Day are supposed to give back thank-you gifts. Douki-chan is hopeful that she'll get one from Douki-kun.

6.TitleEnglish: My Coworker Who Received An Embarrassing Selfie
6.SummaryEnglish: Douki-chan accidentally sends her cosplay selfie to Douki-kun. Out of embarrassment, she calls in sick. But she gets this weird feeling and decides to go to work.

7.TitleEnglish: A Coworker Who Goes All-Out With Seductive Lingerie
7.SummaryEnglish: Douki-chan puts on the best lingerie to tell Douki-kun how she really feels. However, another unexpected rival shows up.

8.TitleEnglish: They Clash!! The Junior Coworker VS The Business Client Senpai!
8.SummaryEnglish: Dinner with Douki-kun has now turned into drinking with Douki-chan's rivals. But Douki-kun pulls her aside to be alone with her.

9.SummaryEnglish: The day is breaking, and our heroine wakes up naked in her bed! What could have happened the night she was about to declare her feelings to our hero?

10.TitleEnglish: A Coworker Who's Excited About A Poolside Date
10.SummaryEnglish: One of the office colleagues is looking for someone to accompany her to the pool, so she decides to invite our two protagonists.

11.TitleEnglish: It Finally Bears Fruit!! Good For You, Douki-Chan
11.SummaryEnglish: Douki-chan and Douki-kun are at a wedding, and some guys hit on Douki-chan.

12.TitleEnglish: That's What I'm Talking About, Douki-Kun
12.SummaryEnglish: At a wedding party, the colleague is hoping to get attention from her crush again. But when she suddenly had to cosplay again, this wish was immediately gone...
